data.description: 1 LEVEL LOG HOME!!!! 6.1 Whole Acres WITH Privacy and Seclusion in a Quiet Subdivision minutes from Great Falls. This custom log home features 3bed-2 bath that glows with the warmth that a log home gives. The home has an open Kitchen, Oversized(32x28) 2 car garage that is heated. GREAT views of the Highwoods, Little Belt and the Rocky Mountain Front. Please call Talbert Bryan; 406-868-5157,or your Real Estate Professional Please call agent for an Appointment
